parameters: Welcome to the hall of a one-night dream, Somnium...
Although it's a place like this, I can at least wear proper clothes...

The drinks, umm... are complimentary... Please, make yourself
comfortable...

Owner, it's a strange feeling... I can't quite put it into words, but
it's like she's not quite like a normal person...
Well, as long as she pays me my salary properly, anything is fine.

This is the stage. Please relax in the dining area until the
performance starts.

Hmm... You have gathered good girls. The cooking is not bad either. I
wonder if it was worth coming all the way by ship.
Oh... So you dance like that? Nice...

I heard a rumor that this place is being operated without permission
from the lord... But it seems that something called the Jimet Company
is backing it up and running things smoothly.

That being said, there's something strange about the male owner...
Well, as long as we can enjoy ourselves, it's fine.
I think you're going a bit too far, aren't you...?
